t customer complaints.\u000a•Redesigned billing-related workflows, cutting processing time by 18%, and\u000alowering the risk of operational errors.\u000aAssociate (Operations & Strategy), Tech Mahindra\u000a•PROJECT- FLIPKART INDIA\u000a•Customer Support | Operations | E-commerce Support\u000a05/2021 – 05/2022\u000aKolkata\u000a•Handled over 50 customer cases daily, resolving order, delivery, payment, and\u000areturn issues across Flipkart''s e-commerce platform.\u000a•Delivered strategic recommendations that improved support workflows,\u000acontributing to a 7% increase in annual revenue.\u000a•Provided 2/7 operational support, ensuring smooth system performance and high\u000acustomer satisfaction.\u000a•Developed a strong understanding of e-commerce operations in the Indian\u000amarket, enhancing service quality and responsiveness.\u000aInternships\u000aAssociate Consultant Intern, Edggi Consulting\u000a•Conducted comprehensive market research and data analysis to identify target\u000acustomer segments, and growth opportunities for the organisation.\u000a•Developed and recommended go-to-market strategies that aligned with business\u000agoals, contributing to improved targeting, and strategic outreach efforts.\u000a01/2025 – 03/2025\u000aRemote\u000aSales Intern, Coolberg\u000a•Developed and managed relationships with over 50 retail and HoReCa (Hotels,\u000aRestaurants, Cafes) clients, supporting revenue growth and increasing brand\u000apresence.\u000a•Implemented B2B sales strategies across General Trade and HoReCa channels,\u000aexceeding sales targets and achieving 2nd rank among interns in Kolkata.\u000a04/2024 – 06/2024\u000aKolkata\u000aSKILLS\u000aOperational Management\u000aProject Management\u000aVendor Management\u000aData Analysis\u000aProcess Optimization\u000aStakeholder Management\u000aGTM Strategies\u000aStrategic Execution\u000aAWARDS & HONOURS\u000aLetter of Appreciation, Capgemini as well as US Client.\u000aTech Mahindra''s Top Performer, Newsletter Recognition\u000aCertificates\u000aLEAN SIX SIGMA POWER BI DESKTOP'),NULL);
