 & Written Communication | Telephone Etiquette |\u000aProfessionalism | Patience | Emotional Intelligence\u000a Technical Proficiency: Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, Word, PowerPoint, Outlook) | Administrative Writing | Proofreading |\u000aTyping & Editing\u000a Organizational & Analytical Skills: Problem-Solving | Attention to Detail | Multitasking | Resourcefulness | Flexibility |\u000aDiscretion & Judgment\u000a Business Support & Logistics: Supply & Stationery Management | Office Procedures | Anticipating Needs | Teamwork |\u000aReporting & Analysis\u000aTECHNICAL SKILLS\u000a HR & Talent Management: ATS & HRMS Tools | Recruitment & Onboarding | Performance Management | Compensation &\u000aBenefits | Payroll Processing | Training & Development\u000a Administrative & Business Operations: Office Management | Reporting & Documentation | Travel & Logistics Coordination\u000a| Inventory & Supply Chain Management\u000a Customer Service & Communication: Client Relationship Management | Professional Correspondence | Verbal & Written\u000aCommunication | Employee Engagement\u000a Software & Tools: Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, Word, PowerPoint, Outlook) | HRMS | CRM Tools | Administrative Writing\u000a| Data Entry | Proofreading\u000a Analytical & Problem-Solving: Business Analysis | HR Policy Compliance | Process Optimization | Attention to Detail |\u000aMultitasking\u000aCAREER HIGHLIGHTS\u000a Proven HR Expertise: Managed end-to-end recruitment, talent acquisition, performance appraisal, and training &\u000adevelopment to enhance workforce efficiency.\u000a Operational Efficiency: Streamlined HR processes, office administration, and business operations, leading to improved\u000aproductivity and compliance.\u000a Strategic Leadership: Spearheaded employee engagement programs, workforce planning, and business growth initiatives,\u000acontributing to long-term organizational success.\u000a Client & Stakeholder Management: Built and maintained strong relation