ptimized CRM and operational workflows to improve lead-to-enrollment conversion.\u000a• Automated performance reporting and reduced manual errors, improving TAT.\u000a• Collaborated with sales, marketing, and content teams for smooth campaign execution.\u000a• Conducted data-driven analysis on cancellations, payment trends, and satisfaction metrics.\u000a• Implemented process automation that reduced turnaround time by 20%.\u000aPre-Sales Engineer – Skill Lync (Apr 2022 – Dec 2022)\u000a• Delivered impactful demos and webinars aligned with client and learner goals.\u000a• Partnered with sales teams to improve lead conversion and client engagement.\u000a• Analyzed feedback to enhance pre-sales content, demos, and delivery experience.\u000aEducation\u000aB.Tech in Civil Engineering, B. S. Abdur Rahman Crescent Institute Of Science and\u000aTechnology (2018 – 2022) – CGPA: 8.6/10\u000a\u000a12th Grade, Narayana Jr College – 94.6%\u000a10th Grade, Kids Patasala – 85%\u000aAchievements\u000a• Reduced Sales- Operations handover TAT by 15% and improved on-time payments by\u000a10%.\u000a• Helped maintain 85%+ CSAT during Installation phase.\u000a• Led social initiatives and volunteered for NGO programs.\u000a• Represented college in sports and cultural events.\u000aLanguages\u000aTelugu, Tamil, English, Hindi\u000aInterests\u000aLearning new tools and systems | Travelling | Puzzles | Socializing'),NULL);
