cross-functional teams of developers, data scientists and product designers to oversee product\u000aconceptualization and prototype development.\u000a• Invested personal capital to fund product development and early-stage R&D activities.\u000a• An early-stage AI startup focused on building machine learning solutions for business process automation.\u000aSKILLS\u000a• Communication\u000a• Creativity\u000a• Team work & leadership\u000a• Project management\u000a• Problem solving\u000a• Time management\u000a• Critical Thinking\u000a• Business Analysis\u000aPROJECTS\u000aProject Title: Research project on Cryptocurrency Blockchain 2021\u000a• Developed an exceptional research paper on cryptocurrency, recognized as the best in its field.\u000a• Demonstrated a profound understanding of cryptocurrency concepts and technologies through\u000acomprehensive analysis.\u000a• Received accolades and recognition from esteemed individuals and organization for the paper’s publication\u000ato the field of blockchain.\u000aEDUCATION\u000aUniversity Name: REVA University 2018 – 2021\u000aCourse: BSc Computer Science, CGPA – 6.9\u000aCollege Name: Bharathi Junior College 2015 – 2017\u000aCourse: MPC, CGPA – 7.4\u000aCERTIFICATIONS\u000a• Certified Scrum Product Owner from Scrum Alliance'),NULL);
