uying\u000aInMobi (Glance)\u000a•Drove multiple new client strategies through cross selling and up selling, using data driven insights,\u000aachievening 25% MOM growth.\u000a01/2023 – 06/2025\u000aBangalore, Karnataka\u000a•Executed direct and programmatic campaigns across diverse categories including OTT, Gaming, FMCG, and\u000aFintech, while overseeing revenue and financial closures to ensure maximum revenue optimization.\u000aCampaign Analyst\u000aInMobi (Glance)\u000a•Owned end-to-end campaign operations for APAC and SEA clients post-onboarding, ensuring smooth\u000aexecution and alignment with client objectives.\u000a02/2022 – 12/2022\u000aBangalore, Karnataka\u000a•Improved campaign efficiency and performance through deep funnel analysis and cohort-based targeting,\u000aleveraging diverse signals for optimization.\u000aAssociate, Student Success\u000aUpGrad\u000a•Acted as the primary point of contact for 300+ learners per batch, maintaining regular communication to\u000aaddress queries, provide guidance, and improve program completion rates through data-driven analysis of\u000alearner trends and engagement patterns.\u000a07/2021 – 01/2022\u000aHyderabad, Telangana\u000a•Facilitated seamless coordination with cross-functional stakeholders, including professors and industry\u000aleaders, to ensure the successful delivery of sessions and enhance the overall learning experience.\u000aBusiness Development Intern\u000aGoMechanic\u000a•Supported garage partners and assisted regional account managers in the onboarding and servicing of clients,\u000aensuring smooth partnership operations.\u000a03/2021 – 07/2021\u000aHyderabad, Telangana\u000a•Contributed to streamlining spare parts logistics and enhancing client relationship management processes for\u000abetter service delivery.\u000aEDUCATION\u000aB.Tech – Chemical Engineering\u000aManipal Institute of Technology\u000aGPA: 6.86 / 10\u000a08/2016 – 05/2021\u000aManipal, Karnataka\u000aIntermediate\u000aSri Chaitanya Na