ics & Language: Advanced Excel, VBA, Python, SQL, Power BI, Tableau\u000aTools & Methodologies: Jira, Trello, MS Project, Agile, Scrum\u000aLANGUAGES\u000aEnglish (Primary Language); Hindi (Bilingual); Spanish (Beginner); Sanskrit (Beginner)'),NULL);
