Led cross-functional projects and business analysis for a $120M portfolio, managing budgets, resource allocation, delivery\u000aplanning, and coordinating executive calendars and travel across multiple digital and AI-driven initiatives, ensuring timely\u000adelivery with zero escalations.\u000a• Drove digital transformation and product adoption, translating business needs into BRDs/FSDs, defining KPIs, and guiding\u000adevelopment teams on AI-enabled reporting and analytics platforms, enhancing operational efficiency and user satisfaction.\u000a• Managed Founder’s Office and CIO Office initiatives, including strategic reporting, corporate workshops, executive\u000adashboards, and coordination of executive travel and meetings, leveraging AI analytics to support data-driven decisions and\u000astrengthen stakeholder engagement.\u000a• Owned reporting and internal AI programs, implementing dashboards and process improvements for hundreds of users,\u000afostering innovation and aligning business strategy with measurable performance outcomes\u000aUppskill\u000aBusiness Analyst- Summer Internship May 2022 - Jun 2022\u000a• Analyzed business and user data using SQL and Excel to derive insights that informed product strategy, resulting in a 15%\u000aincrease in sales.\u000a• Designed BI dashboards that enabled leadership to track KPIs, leading to a 25% reduction in decision-making time.\u000aMobikasa\u000aSoftware Developer Aug 2020 - Oct 2020\u000a• Developed and implemented 5 front-end features using HTML, JavaScript, AJAX, and JSON, resulting in a 30% increase in user\u000aengagement. Combined with supporting product enhancements by working closely with 3 project managers and 2 sprint\u000ateams, ensuring timely delivery of 12 high-priority features.\u000aEducation\u000aChrist University\u000aMaster of Business Administration in Business Analytics Jun 2021 - May 2023\u000aVIT University\u000aB. Tech in Computer Science & Engineering Jun 2016 - Mar 2020\u000aCertificates\u000a• Google Data Analytics Professional Certificate – Google\u000a• Business Analysis Foundation – LinkedIn\u000a• Analyzing and Visualizing Data with Power BI – Microsoft\u000a• Project Management – Great Learning\u000aAwards & Recognition\u000aInspiring Performance Award- BGSW (Sep 2024)\u000aEvent Lead – Digital & AI Day for Corporate – BGSW (Apr 2025)'),NULL);
